works.description:
Dartz, the Russian tuner that never fails  
to hit the news with its bespoke rides, has now teamed up with Gray Design,  
famous for the Strand Craft Limousine Beach Cruiser, to announce the  
release of the 2012 Dartz Prombron’ Nagel, the world’s first armored  
Sportback SUV designed for pulling yachts. The car will be launched in  
2012, coinciding with many anniversaries for the car brand RussoBalt  
(RussoBaltique), which later became Prombron and then the Dartz Prombron.
